The `orun` documentation site is a docs-only Docusaurus project under `website/`. The production target is Cloudflare Pages.

## Local validation

Install dependencies and run the local dev server:

```bash
cd website
npm install
npm run docs:start
```

Create a production build:

```bash
cd website
npm ci
npm run docs:build
npm run docs:serve
```

