      }
    ]
  },
  "createdAt": "2026-05-31T00:00:00Z"
}
```

## 7.3 `ComponentManifest`

File:

```text
sources/<sourceSnapshotKey>/catalogs/<catalogSnapshotKey>/components/<componentName>/manifest.json
```

Schema:

```json
