## 6. Help-text fixtures

Every `orun catalog *` subcommand has a `--help` golden file:

```text
cmd/orun/testdata/help/catalog/
  refresh.txt
  list.txt
  describe.txt
  tree.txt
  diff.txt
  history.txt
  refs.txt
  validate.txt
